2009年1月和2月，[[以色列空军|以色列空军]]'''在[[苏丹|苏丹]]进行了两次空袭'''，在[[红海|红海]]进行了一次空袭，据称是[[以色列|以色列]]针对通过苏丹走私到加沙地带的伊朗武器进行的。<ref>{{cite news |title=Exclusive: Three Israeli Airstrikes Against Sudan |url=http://blogs.abcnews.com/politicalradar/2009/03/exclusive-three.html |publisher=ABC News |date=2009-03-27 |accessdate=2009-03-28 |archive-date=2009-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090329094645/http://blogs.abcnews.com/politicalradar/2009/03/exclusive-three.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=haaretz0328>{{cite news |title=Report: Israel carried out 3 attacks on Sudan arms smugglers |url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1074457.html |publisher=Haaretz |date=2009-03-28 |accessdate=2009-03-28 |archive-date=2009-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090330054159/http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1074457.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>以色列政府暗示，以色列部队参与了这一事件。<ref>{{cite news |first=Paul |last=Wood |title=Did Israel carry out Sudan strike? |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/7966865.stm |publisher=BBC News |date=2009-03-26 |accessdate=2009-12-30 |archive-date=2018-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181121020923/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/7966865.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Mystery over Sudan 'air strike' |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/7966627.stm |publisher=BBC News |date=2009-03-26 |accessdate=2009-12-30 |archive-date=2019-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190807045835/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/africa/7966627.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==突袭==
以色列《[[国土报|国土报]]》的军事记者阿莫斯•哈雷尔写道，对苏丹进行打击的决定显然源于一种信念，即伊朗将向加沙地带运入大量武器，可能是70公里射程的Fajr-3火箭。《星期日泰晤士报》的一篇报道还说，这些卡车正在运送Fajr-3火箭，这些火箭是由伊朗革命卫队运到苏丹港，交给当地走私者的。这篇文章还说，空袭是由无人驾驶的赫耳墨斯450进行的。<ref>{{cite news |first=Uzi |last=Mahnaimi |title=Israeli drones destroy rocket-smuggling convoys in Sudan |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/africa/article5993093.ece |publisher=The Sunday Times |accessdate=2009-03-29 |date=2009-03-29 |location=London |archive-date=2020-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626104053/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，《时代周刊》报道称，这次袭击是由F-16战斗机和无人机护航的。<ref>{{cite news |title=How Israel Foiled an Arms Convoy Bound for Hamas |url=http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,1888352,00.html |publisher=TIME |date=2009-03-30 |accessdate=2009-03-31 |archive-date=2013-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826185352/http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,1888352,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>4月8日，《[[新消息报|新消息报]]》援引美国消息来源报道称，[[以色列海军|以色列海军]][[第13突击队|第13突击队]]部队参与了此次行动，其中包括袭击一艘停靠在苏丹的伊朗军船。<ref name=naval>{{Cite news| title = Report: Naval commando forces involved in Sudan strike| work = Ynetnews| accessdate = 2009-04-08| date = 2009-04-08| url = http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3699142,00.html| archive-date = 2021-01-16| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210116104941/https://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-3699142,00.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>

以色列空军司令埃坦·本-埃利亚胡说，这种攻击的主要困难是精确的情报。要到达目标，需要飞行约两个半小时，可能沿着红海海岸沿南方向飞行，在沙特和埃及的雷达下，并进行空中加油。<ref name=harel>{{Cite news| last = Harel| first = Amos| title = Sudan strike won't make Iran give up on Hamas| work = Haaretz| accessdate = 2009-03-28| date = 2009-03-27| url = http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1074314.html| archive-date = 2009-04-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090422085850/http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/1074314.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>

3月25日，哥伦比亚广播公司新闻首次在大众媒体上提到了这起事件。<ref>{{cite news |first=Dan |last=Raviv |title=U.S. Accused Of Killing 39 In Sudan Strike |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/blogs/2009/03/25/world/worldwatch/entry4892589.shtml |work=World Watch |publisher=CBS News |date=2009-03-25 |accessdate=2009-12-30 |archive-date=2009-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090329045924/http://www.cbsnews.com/blogs/2009/03/25/world/worldwatch/entry4892589.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>5月26日，苏丹国防部长阿卜杜勒·拉希姆·穆罕默德·侯赛因声称，这支由1000名平民组成的车队参与了“与埃及边境的走私活动”。部长声称有119人被杀；其中有56名走私者和63名来自埃塞俄比亚、索马里和其他民族的偷渡者。<ref name=reuters>{{cite news |title=Air strike on Sudan convoy killed 119: state media |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idUSTRE54O4FA20090525 |publisher=Reuters |date=2009-05-25 |accessdate=2009-12-30 |first=Andrew |last=Heavens |archive-date=2021-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114032735/https://www.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idUSTRE54O4FA20090525 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

